claim.claim-text:
A method, comprising:
receiving an input of a character from a virtual keyboard displayed on a display;
generating at least two sets of predicted input characters based on the input character;
displaying at least two of the generated sets of predicted input characters at an input field, wherein each displayed set is displayed at a position in a defined arrangement; and
selecting one of the displayed sets of predicted input characters in accordance with a gesture received at a partition of the virtual keyboard.

An electronic device, comprising:
a processor;
a display coupled to the processor;
wherein the processor is configured to perform the method of any one of claims 1 to 10.
